{
  "id": "RAW_7fd223",
  "title": "【实践】AI 产品如何定价？硅谷定价大师的四象限法则",
  "url": "https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s?__biz=MzE5OTE3NTEyMA==&mid=2247485110&idx=1&sn=a4a4c8fc6e5ee7c59f9de68bd5dc971e",
  "date": "2025-09-15 10:08:00",
  "author": "AI炼金术",
  "siteName": "AI炼金术",
  "content": "<html>\n <head></head>\n <body>\n  <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;font-weight:400;letter-spacing:2.5px;font-size:15px;line-height:2;font-style:normal;box-sizing:border-box;text-align:justify;\">\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 15px;letter-spacing: 2px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 27px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">来源</span></strong></span><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Source</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;justify-content: flex-start;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 0px 0px 10px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;width: auto;vertical-align: top;align-self: flex-start;flex: 100 100 0%;border-style: solid;border-width: 0px 0px 0px 2px;border-color: rgb(242, 227, 84) rgb(242, 227, 84) rgb(242, 227, 84) rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 8px 11px 0px;margin: 0px 0px 0px 16px;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: justify;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">标题：&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Pricing AI: How to price in the age of AI</span></span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">分享者：&nbsp;</span></span><span style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Madhavan Ramanujam</span></span></strong></p>\n      <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\"><span textstyle=\"\"><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nz2Q6_u8Zgg\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=nz2Q6_u8Zgg</a></span></span></span></strong></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"font-size: 14px;line-height: 1.8;letter-spacing: 2px;padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">现在融资不容易，做产品一定要考虑怎么赚钱，考虑赚钱第一步就是设计定价。这个分享里面除了有四象限这种套路之外，还有对创始人非常深刻的提醒。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;letter-spacing:2px;font-size:14px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 25px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">要点</span></b></span><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"></b><span style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Key Takeaways</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"font-size: 14px;letter-spacing: 2px;padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></p>\n   <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">每一个技术浪潮，都会催生新的定价模型创新</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 产品的定价，正在从“购买软件”变为“购买结果”</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">成功的定价，始于早期对用户“支付意愿”的测试</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">别把 POC 当技术验证，把它当成商业案例的共同探索</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 定价的圣杯，是高自主性、高可归因性的“按结果付费”</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">创始人最大的心魔，是害怕涨价，但这往往是内部情绪</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n    <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">防止客户流失的最佳方式，是在一开始就吸引对的人</span></span></p>\n    </li>\n   </ul>\n   <p></p>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">1</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;font-size: 14px;line-height: 2;letter-spacing: 2.5px;padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">如何像测试 PMF 一样</span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">测试“支付意愿”？</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=01f6ba05&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIftaoQkeVick7fkNKpjU3THhxIdOnsLPlQicuReh9lbgcZp2bAQsApByaSqvzEJZl4QLFuCQE5thng%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Madhavan Ramanujam</span></span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">：“创始人必须尽早与客户展开关于‘支付意愿’的对话，就像他们测试产品市场契合度一样。”</span></span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Madhavan Ramanujam</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">：“你可以问客户三个价格：‘可接受的’，‘昂贵的’，和‘贵得离谱的’，这能帮你理解他们的心理阈值。”</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我们花了大量时间验证用户是否需要我们的产品，却很少花时间去验证他们愿意为之付多少钱。Madhavan 强调，对“支付意愿”的测试，应该和对 PMF 的测试一样，贯穿产品开发的早期阶段。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">他分享了一个非常实用的访谈技巧。当你和潜在客户讨论价格时，不要直接问“你愿意付多少钱”，因为这很难得到真实的答案。相反，你可以像 Superhuman 在早期做的那样，询问三个关键的价格点：</span></p>\n    <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">可接受的价格 (Acceptable Price):&nbsp;</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">你认为这个产品的公允价值是多少？</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">昂贵的价格 (Expensive Price):</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在哪个价格点，你会觉得有点贵，需要向上级申请一下？</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">贵得离谱的价格 (Prohibitively Expensive Price):</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;在哪个价格点，你会觉得完全不值，根本不会考虑购买？</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ol>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">通过这三个问题，你可以在多个用户中找到价格共识的区间，它清晰地揭示了用户的心理价格锚点，为你制定初始价格提供了极其宝贵的数据支撑。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">2</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">别做技术验证，要做商业案例验证</span></strong></p>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.423148148148148\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=dde90607&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIftaoQkeVick7fkNKpjU3THicVjUMAheq4oIJudvmsrGkwdFOLPDm3heMFNqXC6HQltA9aoYGj3ATQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 11px;vertical-align: super;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Madhavan Ramanujam</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 11px;vertical-align: super;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">：“你应该将概念验证（POC, Proof of Concept）定义为一个商业案例的共同验证，而不仅仅是技术验证。”</span></span></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Madhavan Ramanujam</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">：“在 POC 阶段，你需要和客户共同创建一个投资回报率 (ROI, Return on Investment) 模型，来证明产品的价值，并确保他们的认可。”</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">在 B2B 销售中，POC 是一个关键环节，但许多 AI 创业公司在这里犯了致命错误。他们把 POC 变成了免费的技术能力展示，任由客户的技术团队进行测试，却很少涉及业务和财务部门。结果往往是，技术团队觉得产品很酷，但因为无法量化其商业价值，最终项目不了了之。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Madhavan 建议，</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">从第一天起，就要把 POC 的框架从“技术验证”升级为“商业案例验证”</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。你需要找到客户方愿意与你共同探索商业价值的“盟友”，和他一起建立一个 ROI 模型。这个模型需要清晰地计算出，你的 AI 产品将如何为他们带来收入增长、成本节约或机会成本的降低。当这个 ROI 模型是由你和客户共同创建并认可的，POC 的成功就不再是你单方面的说辞，而是客户内部的共识，这将极大地推动最终的采购决策。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">3</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 定价的四象限法则</span></strong></p>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=85620f81&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIftaoQkeVick7fkNKpjU3THBAiadEU4s6zlwbzIw7iaTicbBKXazA6Sx7cM4uPXEQdb6G0UD80Nl97Pw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 14px;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Madhavan Ramanujam：“我用一个 2x2 的四象限矩阵来决定正确的定价模型，Y 轴是自主性（Autonomy），X 轴是可归因性（Attribution）。”</span></span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">这是整个分享中最核心、最精彩的模型。Madhavan 认为，AI 产品的定价模式，主要由两个关键维度决定：</span></p>\n    <ol style=\"list-style-type: decimal;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-1\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">自主性 (Autonomy):</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;AI 在多大程度上能独立完成工作，无需人工干预？</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">可归因性 (Attribution):</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;AI 创造的价值，能在多大程度上被清晰地衡量和归因？</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ol>\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">由此构成了四个象限：</span></p>\n    <ul style=\"list-style-type: disc;box-sizing: border-box;padding-left: 20px;list-style-position: outside;\" class=\"list-paddingleft-2\">\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">左下（低自主，低归因）</span></span></strong><span leaf=\"\">: 传统的</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">按座付费 (Per-seat) 模型。</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">例如 Slack，它是一个协作工具，价值难以量化到个人。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">右下（低自主，高归因）:</span></strong></span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;混合模式 (Hybrid)</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">，即“按座付费 + 按用量付费”。例如编程助手 Cursor，你能清晰地看到它为你节省了多少工作量。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">左上（高自主，低归因）</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">: 纯粹的</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">按用量付费 (Usage-based)&nbsp;</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">模型。例如 Twilio，它在后台自主运行，但其价值是基础设施层面的，难以直接归因到最终业务结果。</span></p>\n     </li>\n     <li style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">右上（高自主，高归因）</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">: 定价的圣杯——</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">按结果付费 (Outcome-based)</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">&nbsp;模型。例如前面提到的 AI 客服 Fin，它完全自主地解决客户问题，且结果（解决的问题数）清晰可衡量。这是 AI 变现的终极形态。</span></p>\n     </li>\n    </ul>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">4</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <p style=\"text-align: center;white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">“按结果付费”：AI 变现的圣杯</span></strong></p>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.386111111111111\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=92d8ba26&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIftaoQkeVick7fkNKpjU3THetW8gnXSKViaGD2ZSyFFAF9HQicXeibajHBR6fBiaFOhOjF0XkHNvw4BYQ%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Madhavan Ramanujam</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">：“‘按结果付费’并非适用于所有产品，它需要清晰的价值归因和高度自主的操作。虽然目前只有不到 5% 的 AI 公司采用，但我预测未来三年会增长到 25-30%。”</span></sup><sub style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"></sub></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">“按结果付费”是所有 AI 创业者梦寐以求的模式，因为它完美地将产品的收费与为客户创造的价值挂钩，从根本上消除了客户的购买阻力。客户不再是为“软件”付费，而是为“利润”付费。</span></span></strong></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">然而，Madhavan 也提醒，这种模式的门槛极高。它要求你的产品不仅能自主运行，而且其产生的每一个结果都必须是清晰可衡量的。此外，他特别指出了一个陷阱：警惕那些“偶发性”价值交付的场景。如果你的产品只是偶尔为客户创造一次巨大价值，然后按结果收取高额费用，这会让客户感觉像是被“绑架勒索”，不利于建立长期信任关系。理想的“按结果付费”模型，应该建立在持续、高频的价值交付之上。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">5</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">创业公司的定价护城河</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:18px 25px;margin:-40px 0px 0px;-webkit-transform:translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);display:flex;flex-flow:row;border-color:rgb(160, 160, 160);-o-transform:translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);box-sizing:border-box;border-radius:18px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 5px 5px 0px 0px, rgb(255, 255, 255) 5px 5px 0px 0px inset;transform:translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);overflow:hidden;width:100%;justify-content:flex-end;border-width:1px;-moz-transform:translate3d(-5px, 0px, 0px);border-style:solid;text-align:right;height:auto;\">\n    <div style=\"text-align: justify;font-size: 13px;padding: 0px 15px;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Madhavan Ramanujam</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：“创业公司可以通过提供不同的定价模型来颠覆行业巨头，就像 Netflix 颠覆 Blockbuster 一样。”</span></p>\n     <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Madhavan Ramanujam</span></strong><span leaf=\"\">：“AI 创业公司可以利用‘按结果付费’作为护城河，特别是当行业巨头因为其复杂的系统架构，而难以适应新的商业模式时。”</span></p>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"margin: -32px 0px 10px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n       <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 80px;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img width=\"100%\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"0.698\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"500\" style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=f280547f&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_gif%2FZYtz1MsSQ4RTbytdiaPzIMoicwianRB9t8ZUZic1pDp0mgvl6Ems385uIZmXaibj9Gxxhy9NIv8kRs8DX275yboRQ0g%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dgif\"></p>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">定价本身，就是一种强大的竞争策略。Netflix 挑战 Blockbuster，靠的不是电影更多，而是用包月订阅模式，颠覆了后者的按次租赁 + 滞纳金模式。</span></span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">同样，</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">AI 创业公司面对根深蒂固的行业巨头时，最大的机会之一就是用创新的定价模型进行“降维打击”。巨头们往往被其庞大的、服务于旧定价模式（如按座付费）的系统架构和销售体系所拖累，很难快速转向灵活的“按结果付费”或“按用量付费”模式</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。而创业公司没有历史包袱，可以从第一天起就围绕最先进的商业模式来构建产品和组织。这种“商业模式护城河”，往往比技术护城河更难被跨越。</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"margin-top: 10px;margin-bottom: 10px;text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"display: inline-block;vertical-align: top;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"padding-left: 15px;padding-right: 15px;margin-top: -18px;margin-bottom: -18px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><b style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">6</span></b></p>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"text-align: center;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">创始人最大的心魔：害怕涨价</span></strong></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.4546296296296297\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=a17253da&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIftaoQkeVick7fkNKpjU3THuh8tVlyiaoQ7h7Z7nRQUIQtsdYm1rlYHRILSKyibasHn8mesDEGrwwRw%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n       <div style=\"text-align: justify;color: rgb(160, 160, 160);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Madhavan Ramanujam</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">：“对涨价的抵触，往往是内部的、情绪化的，而非外部的、逻辑性的。”</span></sup></p>\n        <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Madhavan Ramanujam</span></sup></strong><sup style=\"font-size: 11px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">：“防止客户流失的最好方法，不是在最后一刻去挽留，而是在一开始就主动去获取那些天生就倾向于留存更久、参与度更高的客户。”</span></sup></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">许多创始人对涨价怀有天然的恐惧，他们害怕失去客户，害怕被抱怨。但 Madhavan 指出，这种恐惧大多源于创始人自己的不安全感，而非客户的真实反应。只要你的产品在持续迭代、持续为客户创造更多价值，那么适度的涨价就是理所当然的。</span></p>\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">此外，</span><span style=\"box-sizing:border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">他还提出了一个关于“客户流失”的反常识观点。与其在客户即将流失时，用各种折扣和优惠去被动挽留，不如在获客阶段就进行主动筛选。你应该清晰地定义出你的“理想客户画像”（Ideal Customer Profile），他们是那些能从你的产品中获得最大价值、且付费能力和意愿最强的一群人</span></strong></span><span leaf=\"\">。把营销和销售资源，都集中在吸引这些“对的”客户上，你的客户留存率自然会得到质的提升。</span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"padding:0px 15px;letter-spacing:2px;box-sizing:border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"white-space: normal;margin: 0px;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><strong style=\"box-sizing: border-box;\"><span style=\"font-size: 27px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">结语</span></span></strong><span style=\"font-size: 12px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">Closing Thoughts</span></span></p>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"display: flex;width: 100%;flex-flow: column;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <div style=\"z-index: 1;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n     <div style=\"text-align: center;justify-content: center;display: flex;flex-flow: row;margin: 10px 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n      <div style=\"align-self:flex-start;padding:15px;box-shadow:rgb(231, 231, 231) 0px 0px 10px 0px;flex:0 0 auto;display:inline-block;width:98%;vertical-align:top;box-sizing:border-box;height:auto;\">\n       <div style=\"text-align: left;margin: 10px 0px 20px;line-height: 0;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n        <p style=\"max-width: 100%;vertical-align: middle;display: inline-block;line-height: 0;width: 100%;height: auto;box-sizing: border-box;\" nodeleaf=\"\"><img style=\"vertical-align: middle;max-width: 100%;width: 100%;box-sizing: border-box;\" class=\"rich_pages wxw-img\" data-ratio=\"1.25\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-w=\"1080\" src=\"https://wechat2rss.bestblogs.dev/img-proxy/?k=95beb000&amp;u=https%3A%2F%2Fmmbiz.qpic.cn%2Fmmbiz_png%2FBMIuxTte9jIftaoQkeVick7fkNKpjU3THTWeM8xfaBnc8C6LfFlmwN5xujeiatLZTfQzLHJKPCzv7yib8Do87eoicA%2F640%3Fwx_fmt%3Dpng\"></p>\n       </div>\n      </div>\n     </div>\n    </div>\n   </div>\n   <div style=\"color: rgb(114, 114, 114);padding: 0px 15px;box-sizing: border-box;\">\n    <p style=\"margin: 0px 0px 12px;white-space: normal;padding: 0px;box-sizing: border-box;\"><span leaf=\"\">我自己听下来，觉得最有价值的三点是：1. 做 MVP 验证市场的时候，不要光验证可行性和市场接受度，更要验证“用户付不付钱”；2. 别害怕涨价，这种恐惧往往不是现实，而是创始人的心魔——最近听 FinalRound 和 DocSend 创始人分享也听到了佐证的段子；3. 应该用高价倒逼自己，一开始就找最疼的细分市场，逼自己把 ICP 想清楚。</span></p>\n   </div>\n  </div>\n </body>\n</html>",
  "aiSummary": "深入解读 AI 产品定价策略，提出硅谷定价大师的四象限法则，强调以结果为导向的商业模式和创始人克服涨价恐惧的重要性。",
  "oneSentenceSummary": "深入解读 AI 产品定价策略，提出硅谷定价大师的四象限法则，强调以结果为导向的商业模式和创始人克服涨价恐惧的重要性。",
  "summary": "文章详细阐述了 AI 产品在当前融资环境下如何有效定价。作者通过引用硅谷定价大师 Madhavan Ramanujam 的观点，强调了早期测试用户“支付意愿”的重要性，并提供了实用的**“可接受的”、“昂贵的”和“贵得离谱的”**三价格访谈技巧。文章核心提出了 AI 产品定价的“四象限法则”，**该法则由 AI 的“自主性”和“可归因性”两个维度构成，**并据此将定价模式分为按座、混合、按用量和按结果付费。其中，“按结果付费”被视为 AI 变现的“圣杯”，但其实现门槛极高。此外，文章还指出创新定价模式是 AI 创业公司对抗巨头的“护城河”，并提醒创始人要克服对涨价的恐惧，专注于吸引“理想客户”。",
  "mainPoints": [
    {
      "point": "早期验证“支付意愿”与 PMF 同等重要",
      "explanation": "创始人应像测试产品市场契合度（PMF）一样，尽早与客户开展关于“支付意愿”的对话，通过询问“可接受的”、“昂贵的”和“贵得离谱的”三个价格点，来理解用户的心理阈值，为定价提供数据支撑。"
    },
    {
      "point": "将 POC 升级为“商业案例验证”",
      "explanation": "在 B2B 销售中，概念验证（POC）不应仅是技术展示，而应是与客户共同探索商业价值、构建投资回报率（ROI）模型的过程，确保客户内部对产品价值的共识，从而推动采购决策。"
    },
    {
      "point": "AI 产品定价的“四象限法则”",
      "explanation": "根据 AI 的“自主性”和“可归因性”两个维度，将定价模式划分为按座付费（低自主、低归因）、混合模式（低自主、高归因）、按用量付费（高自主、低归因）和按结果付费（高自主、高归因），指导企业选择最合适的定价策略。"
    },
    {
      "point": "“按结果付费”是 AI 变现的圣杯",
      "explanation": "这种模式将收费与客户所获价值直接挂钩，但要求产品具备高自主性和清晰可衡量的结果，且价值交付需持续高频，是 AI 产品变现的终极形态，也是创业公司的竞争护城河。"
    },
    {
      "point": "克服涨价恐惧并精准筛选客户",
      "explanation": "创始人应认识到对涨价的恐惧多源于内部情绪，适度涨价是产品价值提升的体现。同时，通过明确“理想客户画像”并在获客阶段主动筛选，而非被动挽留，能有效提升客户留存率。"
    }
  ],
  "keyQuotes": [
    "“创始人必须尽早与客户展开关于'支付意愿'的对话，就像他们测试产品市场契合度一样。”",
    "“你应该将概念验证（POC， Proof of Concept）定义为一个商业案例的共同验证，而不仅仅是技术验证。”",
    "“我用一个 2x2 的四象限矩阵来决定正确的定价模型，Y 轴是自主性（Autonomy），X 轴是可归因性（Attribution）。”",
    "“'按结果付费'并非适用于所有产品，它需要清晰的价值归因和高度自主的操作。虽然目前只有不到 5% 的 AI 公司采用，但我预测未来三年会增长到 25-30%。”",
    "“对涨价的抵触，往往是内部的、情绪化的，而非外部的、逻辑性的。”"
